<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Fresh Harvest Grocery</title>
  <style>
    body { 
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; 
      line-height: 1.6; 
      color: #333; 
      max-width: 600px; 
      margin: 0 auto; 
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f5f0e8;
    }
    .header { 
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3d1c, #2d5a27); 
      padding: 30px; 
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
    }
    .header h1 { 
      color: #7a9e7e; 
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .content { 
      background: #ffffff; 
      padding: 40px 30px;
      border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .btn { 
      display: inline-block; 
      padding: 14px 32px; 
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d5a27, #4a7c44); 
      color: #ffffff; 
      text-decoration: none; 
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer { 
      text-align: center; 
      padding: 30px; 
      color: #666; 
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .highlight {
      color: #2d5a27;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>🌿 FRESH HARVEST</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <h2 style="color: #1a3d1c; margin-top: 0;">Welcome, <%= name %>!</h2>
    
    <p>Thank you for joining <span class="highlight">Fresh Harvest Grocery</span>. We're thrilled to have you as part of our community of fresh food lovers!</p>
    
    <p>With your new account, you can:</p>
    <ul style="padding-left: 20px;">
      <li>Browse our selection of fresh, organic produce</li>
      <li>Order groceries for delivery to your doorstep</li>
      <li>Earn reward coins with every purchase</li>
      <li>Track your orders in real-time</li>
    </ul>
    
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="<%= verificationLink %>" class="btn">Verify Your Email</a>
    </div>
    
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; margin-top: 30px;">
      If you didn't create this account, please ignore this email.
    </p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p><strong>Fresh Harvest Grocery</strong></p>
    <p>Nairobi, Kenya | orders@freshharvest.app | 0113 323 234</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
      This email was sent to you because you registered on our website.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
